    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine. Imagine the scent of aged saddle leather and the tactile click of chrome switches under your fingertips. Every curve of its silhouette was designed to catch the golden hour light on a winding coastal road. It breathes with a soulful purr that modern engines have long forgotten. This masterpiece has been preserved like a secret, waiting for a driver who understands that true beauty isn't about perfection\u2014it's about the stories told in every polished reflection. It stands ready to turn every mundane errand into a cinematic escape.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
