    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this truly pristine, showroom-quality vehicle. Meticulously maintained and presented in unrivaled condition, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior, reflects a standard of care that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This is an investment-grade opportunity for a driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
