    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find its next home. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed, and treated with the kind of love only a true car person understands. It\u2019s in stunning shape, looking and driving just like it did when it first left the showroom. Aside from the tiniest, barely-there stone chip from one of our weekend drives, it is practically perfect. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been cherished and is ready for the open road, come on by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
